ğŸ“Œ 7. When to Use CrewAI?

Use CrewAI when:

* Task needs multiple specialists
* Clear role separation is required
* Human-like collaboration is desired
* Structured AI teams are needed

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

âš ï¸ Common Beginner Mistakes

* Giving vague goals
* Overlapping agent roles
* Too many agents for simple tasks
* No clear task sequencing

